response.original_title: Rock and Roll Hall of Fame 2011 Induction Ceremony
response.overview: The performer Inductees are:  · Alice Cooper will be inducted by Rob Zombie (White Zombie)  · Neil Diamond will be inducted by Paul Simon  · Dr. John will be inducted by John Legend  · Darlene Love will be inducted by Bette Midler  · Tom Waits will be inducted by Neil Young  Ahmet Ertegun Award recipients (nonperformers):  · Jac Holzman will be inducted by John Densmore (the Doors)  · Art Rupe will be inducted by Lloyd Price  The Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Award for Musical Excellence (previously the Sidemen category):  · Leon Russell will be inducted by Elton John
response.title: Rock and Roll Hall of Fame 2011 Induction Ceremony
